  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Keen to learn &amp; develop into a Professional Pet Groomer but do not possess any relevant experience yet</li>\n  <li>Must be an effective team-player with good communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Able to handle dogs (small &amp; large), cats and rabbits with different temperaments</li>\n  <li>Able to work on weekends and public holidays</li>\n  <li>Must have perseverance, love, patience and passion while working with pets</li>\n  <li>Willing to accept teaching from the mentors and work assigned from time to time</li>\n  <li>Maintain Cleanliness</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Singaporean, PR, or Work Permit are welcome to apply.</p>",
